Regexp-CharClass-Common version 2009040201
==========================================

DESCRIPTION

This module provides properties to be used in regular expressions.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires Perl 5.10 or later.

